57.6	Drug_addiction	Substance dependence	The section about substance dependence in the Diagnostic and Statistical Manual of Mental Disorders (more specifically, the 2000 "text revision", the DSM-IV-TR) does not use the word addiction at all. It explains:	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/OCD_handwash.jpg/140px-OCD_handwash.jpg
